# Provider layout (depth)

Target module tree for depth venues:

```
providers::depth
├── binance
│   ├── spot      ← Binance spot (`--sources binance:SYMBOL`)
│   └── usd_m     ← move from `binance_usd_m.rs` (WP follow-up)
└── <venue>/…     ← register new labels in `Provider::from_label` + wire in `run_global_book_stream`
```

## Done (WP-003)

- [x] move binance to `depth::binance::spot`
- [x] accept arbitrary `--sources provider:SYMBOL` labels via `Provider::Registered`
- [x] keep `binance` / `binance-usd-m` parsing and streaming unchanged

## Next

- [ ] move `binance_usd_m.rs` to `depth::binance::usd_m`
- [ ] add rpi support (WP-004)
- [ ] wire third venue: implement `Endpoints<Depth>`, add to `run_global_book_stream` match
